relation: ThinkPad and Lenovo 65W AC Adapter - with US / Canada / LA Line Cord
pageTitle: ThinkPad and Lenovo 65W AC Adapter - with US / Canada / LA Line Cord | 40Y7696 | Lenovo | CA
textBeforeTable: Backed by Lenovo's limited warranty with renowned Service and Support available from IBM Compatible with all ThinkPad X Series laptops and with select ThinkPad Edge, R, T, and Z60 Series and Lenovo 3000 laptops (with integrated graphics only).  Also compatible with the ThinkPad Essential Port Replicator. US/Canada and Japan adapter models are 2-pin; all other country adapter models are 3-pin Same specifications as the standard 65W AC adapter that ships with select ThinkPad and Lenovo systems.  It is the smallest adapter currently available from Lenovo. Have power when you need it, where you need it, anytime with the ThinkPad and Lenovo 65W AC Adapter. Keep one on your desk, another at home, and save your batteries for the road.
